    "text": "On the evening of 21.03.2026, officers from the Hungama Police Station conducted a raid in the Mamadala area of the Ambalantota Police Division based on received information. During the operation, a suspect was taken into custody for the illegal possession of 2,200 liters (11 barrels) of diesel without a valid permit and was subsequently handed over to the Ambalantota Police Station. The suspect is an 80-year-old resident of Jansagama, Mamadala. Further investigations are being carried out by the Ambalantota Police. Police Media Division",
